
"smart_sources:Research/@shang_effects_2015.md": {"path":"Research/@shang_effects_2015.md","last_embed":{"hash":null},"embeddings":{},"last_read":{"hash":"1kqtx9t","at":1774951884830},"class_name":"SmartSource","last_import":{"mtime":1774951829104,"size":3592,"at":1774951884831,"hash":"1kqtx9t"},"blocks":{"#---frontmatter---":[1,93],"#Effects of dietary polysaccharides from the submerged fermentation concentrate of Hericium caput-medusae (Bull.:Fr.) Pers. on fat deposition in broilers.":[95,99],"#Effects of dietary polysaccharides from the submerged fermentation concentrate of Hericium caput-medusae (Bull.:Fr.) Pers. on fat deposition in broilers.#{1}":[97,99]},"outlinks":[{"title":"Author/Hongmei Shang","target":"Author/Hongmei Shang","line":72},{"title":"Author/Hong Mei Shang","target":"Author/Hong Mei Shang","line":73},{"title":"Author/Hui Song","target":"Author/Hui Song","line":74},{"title":"Author/Hui Song","target":"Author/Hui Song","line":75},{"title":"Author/Si Jie Shen","target":"Author/Si Jie Shen","line":76},{"title":"Author/Si Jie Shen","target":"Author/Si Jie Shen","line":77},{"title":"Author/Xu Yao","target":"Author/Xu Yao","line":78},{"title":"Author/Xu Yao","target":"Author/Xu Yao","line":79},{"title":"Author/Bo Wu","target":"Author/Bo Wu","line":80},{"title":"Author/Bo Wu","target":"Author/Bo Wu","line":81},{"title":"Author/Bo Wu","target":"Author/Bo Wu","line":82},{"title":"Author/Li Na Wang","target":"Author/Li Na Wang","line":83},{"title":"Author/Li Na Wang","target":"Author/Li Na Wang","line":84},{"title":"Author/Yun Jiang","target":"Author/Yun Jiang","line":85},{"title":"Author/Yun Yao Jiang","target":"Author/Yun Yao Jiang","line":86},{"title":"Author/Guo Dong Ding","target":"Author/Guo Dong Ding","line":87},{"title":"Author/Guo Dong Ding","target":"Author/Guo Dong Ding","line":88},{"title":"PDF","target":"biblib/shang_effects_2015/shang_effects_2015.pdf","line":90}],"metadata":{"id":"shang_effects_2015","type":"article-journal","title":"Effects of dietary polysaccharides from the submerged fermentation concentrate of Hericium caput-medusae (Bull.:Fr.) Pers. on fat deposition in broilers.","issued":{"date-parts":[[2015]]},"DOI":"10.1002/jsfa.6711","container-title":"Journal of the Science of Food and Agriculture","abstract":"BACKGROUND The present study was conducted to investigate the lipid-lowering effect of polysaccharides from the submerged fermentation concentrate of Hericium caput-medusae (Bull.:Fr.) Pers. (HFCP) in broilers. A total of 480 female Arbor Acres broilers were randomly divided into four dietary treatments, each consisting of six pens as replicates, and fed diets containing 0 (control), 1, 3 or 5 g kg−1 HFCP. RESULTS The results revealed that the average daily gain of broilers increased (linear (L), P < 0.01; quadratic (Q), P < 0.01) when the HFCP levels increased. The serum cholesterol, triglyceride and low-density lipoprotein cholesterol levels decreased (Q, P < 0.05) while the high-density lipoprotein cholesterol level increased (Q, P < 0.05) when the HFCP levels increased. The caecum Escherichia coli count and pH decreased (Q, P < 0.01) while the lactobacilli count and bifidobacteria count increased (L, P < 0.05; Q, P < 0.05) when the HFCP levels increased. The propionic acid and butyric acid concentrations increased (L, P < 0.001; Q, P < 0.001) while the abdominal fat rate and liver fat content decreased (L, P < 0.01; Q, P < 0.05) when the HFCP levels increased. CONCLUSION Dietary supplementation with HFCP may lead to the development of low abdominal fat of broilers as demanded by health-conscious consumers. © 2014 Society of Chemical Industry","tags":["#literature_note"],"author":[{"family":"Shang","given":"Hongmei","literal":""},{"family":"Shang","given":"Hong Mei","literal":""},{"family":"Song","given":"Hui","literal":""},{"family":"Song","given":"Hui","literal":""},{"family":"Shen","given":"Si Jie","literal":""},{"family":"Shen","given":"Si Jie","literal":""},{"family":"Yao","given":"Xu","literal":""},{"family":"Yao","given":"Xu","literal":""},{"family":"Wu","given":"Bo","literal":""},{"family":"Wu","given":"Bo","literal":""},{"family":"Wu","given":"Bo","literal":""},{"family":"Wang","given":"Li Na","literal":""},{"family":"Wang","given":"Li Na","literal":""},{"family":"Jiang","given":"Yun","literal":""},{"family":"Jiang","given":"Yun Yao","literal":""},{"family":"Ding","given":"Guo Dong","literal":""},{"family":"Ding","given":"Guo Dong","literal":""}],"citation-key":"shang_effects_2015","year":"2015","dateCreated":"2026-03-31","reading-status":"to-read","aliases":["Effects of dietary polysaccharides from the submerged fermentation concentrate of Hericium caput-medusae (Bull.:Fr.) Pers. on fat deposition in broilers."],"author-links":["[[Author/Hongmei Shang]]","[[Author/Hong Mei Shang]]","[[Author/Hui Song]]","[[Author/Hui Song]]","[[Author/Si Jie Shen]]","[[Author/Si Jie Shen]]","[[Author/Xu Yao]]","[[Author/Xu Yao]]","[[Author/Bo Wu]]","[[Author/Bo Wu]]","[[Author/Bo Wu]]","[[Author/Li Na Wang]]","[[Author/Li Na Wang]]","[[Author/Yun Jiang]]","[[Author/Yun Yao Jiang]]","[[Author/Guo Dong Ding]]","[[Author/Guo Dong Ding]]"],"attachment":["[[biblib/shang_effects_2015/shang_effects_2015.pdf|PDF]]"],"related":[[]]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},
